teacheasy.data

Class RichText

  • java.lang.Object
    • teacheasy.data.RichText

  • public class RichText
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates the data that describes a Rich Text Fragment as defined in the TeachEasy digital lesson XML format.
    Version:
    1.0 17 Feb 2015
    Author:
    Alistair Jewers

      • RichText

        public RichText(java.lang.String nText,
        java.lang.String nFont,
        int nFontSize,
        java.lang.String nColor,
        java.lang.String... settings)
        Constructor to create the object from the data parsed from XML.
        Parameters:
        nText - The text string.
        nFont - The font.
        nFontSize - The font size as an integer pt size.
        nColor - The color as a hex string.
        settings - A vararg collection of the various emphasis settings, e.g. bold and italic.
